{"tid":884114,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"推理題 鬥快估 唔怕諗爆頭既入黎 （重開）","createTime":"2018-10-31T10:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T11:29:28.000Z","uid":180281,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0eb56d634c3c4050b3bd8708ab0a5620cbc709cb","tid":884114,"uid":180281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:46:59.000Z","msg":"頭先發現出左D錯...重開<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://mew.reasoning-game.info/gameruleb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmew.reasoning-game.info%2Fgameruleb%2F&d=9f0LvOTZOOmviRGUWSaTmP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=649b68bb\" target=\"_blank\">http://mew.reasoning-game.info/gameruleb/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>簡介:</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qbBjbOG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqbBjbOG.png&h=a8aeb55c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n9名普通囚犯被國王囚在一個環型監獄, 而監獄共10個囚室(Room 1-10, 9人+1個空室)中&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我們而都不知囚犯所在的囚室號碼, 獄長(系統)每過一段時間就會給我們一些線索&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n你能用最少的線索推理出所有囚犯的位置嗎?<br />\n<br />\n<strong>規則:</strong><br />\n獄長(系統)公告的第 1 條線索 = 空囚室的號碼<br />\n獄長(系統)公告的第 2 條線索 = 空囚室的左手面(順時針)的囚人名字<br />\n<br />\n獄長(系統)公告的第 3~N 條線索 = 隨機說一個囚犯 與 一個囚室的距離 (*留意以下圖解)<br />\n注1: 系統隨機是不會說中該囚犯所在的囚室<br />\n注2: 系統隨機問題不會重覆<br />\n<br />\n當所有線索都公告完依然沒有人推理出所有人位置, 遊戲直接結束<br />\n注1: 所有線索 = 頭2條位置 + 9人x9個=81個可能 = 83條<br />\n<br />\n位置圖解:<br />\n囚犯 X 位置非常接近 Y 號<br />\n囚犯 X 位置離 Y 號囚室有點遠<br />\n囚犯 X 位置與 Y 號囚室極之遠<br />\n例如: Y 號囚室為3, 下圖為該囚犯 X 的可能位置:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DzQLRO8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDzQLRO8.png&h=61f391ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新回合：<br />\n線索 1: 2 號囚室是沒有人(空房)<br />\n線索 2: 空囚室的左手面(順時針) 是 囚犯 A<br />\n線索 3: 囚犯 G 位置離 10 號囚室有點遠<br />\n線索 4: 囚犯 I 位置非常接近 10 號囚室<br />\n線索 5: 囚犯 B 位置非常接近 7 號囚室<br />\n線索 6: 囚犯 G 位置非常接近 7 號囚室<br />\n<br />\n（今次有對DB 無錯啦喵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"8e15387c6469ca9671a8beadce740cda826b2f45","tid":884114,"uid":136763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:51:12.000Z","msg":"2 吉 <br />\n3 A"},{"pid":"b665e64d49ba1182793058c811788ddb82ca046d","tid":884114,"uid":673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:51:36.000Z","msg":"A3 B6 G8"},{"pid":"9475a5ba4f2859dfcee0e539a02275d2e3fb0463","tid":884114,"uid":26161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:51:58.000Z","msg":"2吉<br />\n3A<br />\n6B<br />\n8G"},{"pid":"0e326db86feca5a8c5a9c7cf351329c4cdd2e9eb","tid":884114,"uid":136763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:52:09.000Z","msg":"G8"},{"pid":"4d82f203478e758916272d6ec17dcdec59a92312","tid":884114,"uid":136763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:52:19.000Z","msg":"B6"},{"pid":"766b942610822ac8cbf3c661c0748ddf29e8e3b5","tid":884114,"uid":136763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:53:56.000Z","msg":"easy medium hard <br />\nwhich mode is it now？"},{"pid":"23ebe8dcc00e31e57c152e3d1ca0edd5c40d939e","tid":884114,"uid":180281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:53:59.000Z","msg":"我個Program自己行緊 每三分鐘會出一條線索...<br />\n行到咁上下copy過黎<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既可以上去睇睇<br />\n<a href=\"http://mew.reasoning-game.info/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmew.reasoning-game.info%2F&d=9f0LvOTZOOmviRGUWSaTmP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=634fc4e5\" target=\"_blank\">http://mew.reasoning-game.info/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/31/185358_d055b7f677a8ecd82e32c005ba2c4cbd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F31%2F185358_d055b7f677a8ecd82e32c005ba2c4cbd.png&h=84539d38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ff7ff7f80ef4c0d707a828003cd2cac5579063d","tid":884114,"uid":673,"like":0,"dislike":0